<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ title }} | CAET Advanced Handbook</title>
<style>
  /* Light-theme study document — optimized for reading on screen AND print. */
  :root {
    --ink: #1a2332;
    --ink-soft: #4a5568;
    --paper: #fbfaf5;
    --paper-accent: #f5f2e8;
    --rule: #d8d3c3;
    --navy: #0a2540;
    --gold: #8b6914;
    --gold-soft: #f4ead0;
    --red: #8b1a1a;
    --red-soft: #fbe9e7;
    --green: #1b4332;
    --green-soft: #e7f0e5;
    --cyan: #0e4a6e;
    --cyan-soft: #e4f1f8;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 48px 80px;
  }
  header.cover {
    border-bottom: 3px double var(--navy);
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 34px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 8px 0 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 56px 0 12px;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  h3 {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 19px;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 32px 0 10px;
  }
  h4 {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin: 20px 0 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  p { margin: 0 0 16px; }
  ul, ol { margin: 0 0 18px; padding-left: 24px; }
  li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .toc {
    background: var(--paper-accent);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 24px 32px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin: 24px 0 40px;
  }
  .toc h2 { margin-top: 0; border: none; font-size: 18px; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; }
  .toc ol { columns: 2; column-gap: 32px; font-size: 14px; }
  .toc li { margin-bottom: 4px; break-inside: avoid; }
  .toc a { color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; }
  .toc a:hover { text-decoration: underline; color: var(--gold); }
  blockquote.why {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--navy);
    background: var(--gold-soft);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 24px 32px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  blockquote.why p { margin: 0 0 12px; }
  blockquote.why p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .callout {
    padding: 16px 22px;
    margin: 18px 0;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--cyan);
    background: var(--cyan-soft);
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .callout.watching { border-left-color: var(--green); background: var(--green-soft); }
  .callout.mistakes { border-left-color: var(--red); background: var(--red-soft); }
  .callout.theory   { border-left-color: var(--gold); background: var(--gold-soft); }
  .callout strong { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .callout.watching strong { color: var(--green); }
  .callout.mistakes strong { color: var(--red); }
  .callout.theory   strong { color: var(--gold); }
  .callout.info     strong { color: var(--cyan); }
  .key-points { margin: 12px 0 20px; padding-left: 20px; }
  .key-points li { margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.55; }
  dl.glossary { margin: 20px 0; }
  dl.glossary dt { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-top: 14px; font-size: 15px; }
  dl.glossary dd { margin: 4px 0 0 0; padding-left: 0; font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink); }
  .steps { counter-reset: step; padding-left: 0; list-style: none; }
  .steps li { counter-increment: step; padding-left: 44px; position: relative; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.55; }
  .steps li::before {
    content: counter(step);
    position: absolute; left: 0; top: -2px;
    width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--navy); color: white;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .quiz {
    background: var(--cyan-soft);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--cyan);
    padding: 24px 32px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .quiz h3 { margin-top: 0; color: var(--cyan); }
  .quiz ol { margin: 12px 0 0 0; padding-left: 22px; }
  .quiz li { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .answer-key details {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    background: var(--paper);
  }
  .answer-key summary { font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; color: var(--navy); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; }
  .answer-key details[open] summary { margin-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); padding-bottom: 6px; }
  .answer-key p { margin-top: 10px; font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .crosswalk {
    background: var(--paper-accent);
    padding: 18px 24px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    margin: 24px 0;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  footer {
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .section-marker {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700;
    margin: 48px 0 0;
  }
  @media print {
    body { padding: 0.6in 0.75in; background: white; font-size: 11pt; max-width: none; }
    h1 { font-size: 24pt; }
    h2 { font-size: 16pt; page-break-after: avoid; }
    h3 { page-break-after: avoid; }
    .callout, blockquote.why { page-break-inside: avoid; }
    .toc { page-break-after: always; }
    details { page-break-inside: avoid; }
    details[open] > summary ~ * { display: block !important; }
    .answer-key details { border: none; }
    a { color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="cover">
  <div class="eyebrow">CAET Advanced Certification · Student Handbook</div>
  <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Aircraft Electronics Association · Workforce Development Division</p>
</header>

<nav class="toc">
  <h2>Contents</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><a href="#why">Why This Matters</a></li>
    <li><a href="#terms">Key Terms &amp; Definitions</a></li>
    {% for kr in knowledge %}<li><a href="#kr-{{ loop.index }}">{{ kr.heading }}</a></li>{% endfor %}
    {% for t in tasks %}<li><a href="#task-{{ loop.index }}">{{ t.heading }}</a></li>{% endfor %}
    <li><a href="#quiz">Self-Check &amp; Oral Board Practice</a></li>
    {% if written_exam_crosswalk %}<li><a href="#crosswalk">Written Exam Crosswalk</a></li>{% endif %}
  </ol>
</nav>

<section id="why">
  <div class="section-marker">Part I — Orientation</div>
  <h2>Why This Matters</h2>
  {% for para in enrichment.why_this_matters %}
  <blockquote class="why"><p>{{ para }}</p></blockquote>
  {% endfor %}
  {% if intro %}
  <h4>From the PQS Source</h4>
  {% for para in intro %}<p>{{ para }}</p>{% endfor %}
  {% endif %}
</section>

<section id="terms">
  <h2>Key Terms &amp; Definitions</h2>
  <p>Master this vocabulary before continuing. The evaluator expects you to use these terms correctly in the oral board.</p>
  <dl class="glossary">
    {% for kt in enrichment.key_terms %}
    <dt>{{ kt.term }}</dt>
    <dd>{{ kt.definition }}</dd>
    {% endfor %}
  </dl>
</section>

<div class="section-marker">Part II — Knowledge Requirements</div>

{% for kr in knowledge %}
{% set kr_key = kr.heading.split('—')[0].split('–')[0].strip().split(' ')[-1] if kr.heading else '' %}
{% set enrich = enrichment.knowledge_enrichment.get(kr_key, {}) %}
<section id="kr-{{ loop.index }}">
  <h2>{{ kr.heading }}</h2>

  {% if enrich.overview %}
  <p>{{ enrich.overview }}</p>
  {% endif %}

  {% if kr.body %}
  <h4>From the PQS Source</h4>
  <p>{{ kr.body }}</p>
  {% endif %}

  {% if enrich.key_points %}
  <h4>Key Points</h4>
  <ul class="key-points">
    {% for pt in enrich.key_points %}<li>{{ pt }}</li>{% endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% endif %}
</section>
{% endfor %}

<div class="section-marker">Part III — Task Preparation</div>

{% for t in tasks %}
{% set task_key = t.heading.split('—')[0].split('–')[0].strip().split(' ')[-1] if t.heading else '' %}
{% set enrich = enrichment.task_enrichment.get(task_key, {}) %}
<section id="task-{{ loop.index }}">
  <h2>{{ t.heading }}</h2>

  {% if t.body %}
  <p>{{ t.body }}</p>
  {% endif %}

  {% if enrich.step_by_step %}
  <h4>Step-by-Step Procedure</h4>
  <ol class="steps">
    {% for step in enrich.step_by_step %}<li>{{ step }}</li>{% endfor %}
  </ol>
  {% endif %}

  {% if enrich.evaluator_watching_for %}
  <div class="callout watching">
    <strong>Evaluator is watching for</strong>
    <ul>
      {% for item in enrich.evaluator_watching_for %}<li>{{ item }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% if enrich.common_mistakes %}
  <div class="callout mistakes">
    <strong>Common mistakes</strong>
    <ul>
      {% for item in enrich.common_mistakes %}<li>{{ item }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
</section>
{% endfor %}

{% if enrichment.background_theory %}
<div class="section-marker">Part IV — Background Theory</div>
<section id="theory">
  <h2>The Science Behind the Procedures</h2>
  <p>When the oral board examiner asks <em>why</em>, these are the explanations they expect to hear.</p>
  {% for key, text in enrichment.background_theory.items() %}
  <div class="callout theory">
    <strong>{{ key.replace('_', ' ').replace('why ', 'Why ')|title }}</strong>
    <p style="margin-top:8px;">{{ text }}</p>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</section>
{% endif %}

<div class="section-marker">Part V — Self-Check</div>

<section id="quiz">
  <h2>Oral Board Practice Questions</h2>
  <p>Answer each aloud before opening the answer key. Mastery means you can explain it to a non-technical person, not just recite a definition.</p>
  <div class="quiz">
    <h3>Questions</h3>
    <ol>
      {% for q in oral %}<li>{{ q }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </div>

  <h3>Answer Key</h3>
  <div class="answer-key">
    {% for q in oral %}
    {% set qnum = q.split(':')[0].strip() %}
    {% set answer = enrichment.oral_board_answers.get(qnum) %}
    <details>
      <summary>{{ q }}</summary>
      {% if answer %}<p>{{ answer }}</p>{% else %}<p><em>Study the corresponding section of this handbook. Practice articulating the answer aloud.</em></p>{% endif %}
    </details>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{% if written_exam_crosswalk %}
<section id="crosswalk">
  <h2>Written Exam Crosswalk</h2>
  <div class="crosswalk">{{ written_exam_crosswalk }}</div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<footer>
  © 2026 Aircraft Electronics Association · Workforce Development Division.<br>
  Derived from CAET Advanced PQS Training Module with supplementary teaching content authored for instructor use.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
